      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="background:#ffffee; width: 65%; text-align:center">ITIL Role / Sub-Process </th>
        <th style="background:#ffffee;">Compliance Manager </th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="text-align:left;"><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Compliance Management</a><br />
          <i>(no sub-processes specified)</i></td>
        <td>AR </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p>&#160;</p>
  <p><b>Remarks</b> </p>
  <p><span id="Accountable">[1] <i>A: Accountable</i> according to the RACI Model: Those who are ultimately accountable for the correct and thorough completion of the ITIL Compliance Management process.</span> </p>
  <p><span id="Responsible">[2] <i>R: Responsible</i> according to the RACI Model: Those who do the work to achieve a task within ITIL Compliance Management.</span> </p>
